title: Readout of the President's meetings today with Senator Rockefeller and with Senators Bennett and Wyden | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House




September 16, 2009

 



Readout of the President's meetings today with Senator Rockefeller and with Senators Bennett and Wyden




 THE WHITE HOUSE Office of the Press Secretary  ___________________________________________________________________________  For Immediate Release                                                  September 16, 2009 Readout of the President’s meetings today with Senator Rockefeller and with Senators Bennett and Wyden  "The President had constructive meetings today with Senator Rockefeller and with Senators Bennett and Wyden in the Oval Office. These meetings underscore the President's continued commitment to working with senators on both sides of the aisle to pass health insurance reform this year."
